title: Upgraded 2 Bed 2bath Coming soon here at Northern Pines Apartments
posting_body: ['Northern Pines Apartment homes', '774 Northern Ave in Clarkston Georgia', '***COMING SOON***', '***COMING SOON***', 'Late fall ………….Possibly as early as October 2022!!', 'We offer a variety of amenities such as:', 'Upgraded All electric two bedroom two Full bath', 'Washer/Dryer connection', 'Separate Laundry room', 'Patios/Balconies', 'Huge Walk in Closets', 'Central Heating and Air', '*24 Hour emergency Maintenance', '*Fully Equipped kitchen', 'Off Street Parking', 'Updated Flooring', 'Cable Ready', 'Black appliances (in select units)', 'New Blinds and much more.', 'Just minutes away are shopping, restaurants, banking and grocery stores.', 'In addition, do not forget the lovely Stone Mountain Park is close by as well.', 'There is also a BBQ Grilling area and playground with Beautiful Landscaping and off street parking.', 'This huge two bedroom; two full bath is 1100 square feet.', 'Our offices are open Monday/', 'Weds/Friday of each week to assist you with your needs.', 'You will Love our Huge two bedrooms', 'Prices are as low as $1,250.00 Includes water', '774 Northern Ave', 'Clarkston, GA 30021', 'show contact info', 'Our rental qualifications include making three times the amount of the monthly rent, passing a Criminal, credit, rental and employment background check!', 'Equal Housing Opportunity', '*Some Restrictions May Apply and Prices are Subject to Change', '774 Northern Ave.', 'Clarkston GA 30021']
